snippet.title: Danganronpa: Dead End Announcement Trailer + Demo
snippet.description:
16 students are trapped inside the illustrious Reservoir University and are told that they will stay there for the rest of their lives. The only way out? To kill another student and get away with it.

DOWNLOAD THE DEMO: https://djcatproductions.itch.io/danganronpa-dead-end

Keep up with the project on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DanganronpaDE
Discord: https://discord.gg/RBpRTde4ke
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Danganronpa: Dead End is a non-profit visual novel based on the Danganronpa series by Kazutaka Kodaka and is not affiliated with Spike Chunsoft.

Director, Artist, Writer: DjcatProductions https://twitter.com/Djcatproduction
Programmer, Animator, Video Editor: Alenoba https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKs0phLL6Ly_ieAgOhAoUCg
Editor, Writer: GamingFennex https://twitter.com/DRHomecoming
3D Modelling, Texturing: GT https://twitter.com/GT_VA_
Composer: Michael St. Louis https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_MJsK0xmKvn38Q4mK_NH0Q
